          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " For each neutron energy one iron, one background",
                " and one n-p scattering spectrum was registered.",
                " The neutron flux was determined by means of a hydro-",
